Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,QUEUE. Depot Maintenance Throughput Optimizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,LOGCOM use case: AI-driven scheduling for induction sequencing,\Nworkforce, and parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Three depots: MCLB Albany, Barstow, Blount Island Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighty end items ingested from a GCSS-MC stand-in. No data movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Greedy priority-weighted scheduler emits a 30-day Plotly Gantt across\N3 depots.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hero AI layer analyzes the schedule. Structured JSON, then narrative\Nbrief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bottleneck named. Parts cascading effects. Top-5 actions for next 30\Ndays.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tune workforce or parts release on the sidebar — the Gantt re-renders\Nlive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL and the same code runs against an on-prem model.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:01:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Powered by the Kamiwaza Stack. Air-gapped, IL5/IL6 ready.
